   <concept id="FAR_24_103" class="- topic/topic concept/concept " xtrc="">
      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">24.103</ph> Procedures.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <ol id="d1578e13" class="- topic/ol ">
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1600e10">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(a)</ph>
						            The contracting officer shall review requirements to determine whether the contract will involve the design, development, or operation of a system of records on individuals to accomplish an agency function.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d1600e15">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph>
						            If one or more of those tasks will be required, the contracting officer shall-</p>
               <ol id="d1578e32" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1600e21">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
								                Ensure that the contract work statement specifically identifies the system of records on individuals and the design, development, or operation work to be performed; and</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d1600e26">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
								                Make available, in accordance with agency procedures, agency rules and regulation implementing the Act.</p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
         </ol>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
